1
00:00:10,440 --> 00:00:12,100
<font color="yellow">Here I go.</font>

2
00:00:12,100 --> 00:00:13,070
<font color="yellow">(Episode 7)</font>

3
00:00:43,330 --> 00:00:46,270
<font color="yellow">Why can't I grab it?</font>

4
00:00:46,430 --> 00:00:48,600
<font color="yellow">I can see it, but I can't pull it out.</font>

5
00:00:51,630 --> 00:00:53,900
<font color="yellow">Did you put enough pressure?</font>

6
00:00:55,030 --> 00:00:57,200
<font color="yellow">Here, let me try again.</font>

7
00:01:13,430 --> 00:01:16,370
<font color="yellow">You said earlier that it's not my fault...</font>

8
00:01:16,370 --> 00:01:18,330
<font color="yellow">no matter what happens,</font>

9
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:20,930
<font color="yellow">- so don't take it back. - Hey.</font>

10
00:01:21,330 --> 00:01:24,430
<font color="yellow">- How can the goblin's bride... - I said, don't take it back.</font>

11
00:01:24,530 --> 00:01:27,570
<font color="yellow">Just stand still. I'm more surprised than you.</font>

12
00:01:27,570 --> 00:01:29,500
<font color="yellow">I'm standing still. How can I get more still than this?</font>

13
00:01:29,500 --> 00:01:31,100
<font color="yellow">Give me that agreement. I'm going to burn it.</font>

14
00:01:31,100 --> 00:01:32,370
<font color="yellow">Wait.</font>

15
00:01:36,430 --> 00:01:39,300
<font color="yellow">I know what it is. This must be it. I get it now.</font>

16
00:01:39,500 --> 00:01:41,570
<font color="yellow">- What is it? - The cursed prince.</font>

17
00:01:41,570 --> 00:01:42,930
<font color="yellow">You know, the ones in fairy tales?</font>

18
00:01:42,930 --> 00:01:44,170
<font color="yellow">What about them?</font>

19
00:01:46,370 --> 00:01:47,400
<font color="yellow">A kiss.</font>

20
00:02:23,900 --> 00:02:26,530
<font color="yellow">I was just in a rush. Please understand.</font>

21
00:02:29,530 --> 00:02:30,570
<font color="yellow">Open your eyes.</font>

22
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:35,070
<font color="yellow">They are open.</font>

23
00:02:36,270 --> 00:02:37,870
<font color="yellow">What did you...</font>

24
00:02:38,870 --> 00:02:40,000
<font color="yellow">Are you insane?</font>

25
00:02:42,100 --> 00:02:43,400
<font color="yellow">Insane?</font>

26
00:02:43,770 --> 00:02:46,700
<font color="yellow">I tried my best to make you pretty.</font>

27
00:02:46,770 --> 00:02:49,500
<font color="yellow">Do you think I wanted to do it? It was a sacrifice on my part.</font>

28
00:02:49,830 --> 00:02:52,400
<font color="yellow">You must have done it lots of times, but for me...</font>

29
00:02:53,630 --> 00:02:54,730
<font color="yellow">Forget it.</font>

30
00:02:54,870 --> 00:02:57,270
<font color="yellow">- For you, what? - It was my first kiss!</font>

31
00:02:58,500 --> 00:03:00,470
<font color="yellow">I shouldn't have wasted it like that.</font>

32
00:03:02,870 --> 00:03:04,900
<font color="yellow">- Get back here. Let me try again. - No, no.</font>

33
00:03:04,900 --> 00:03:06,300
<font color="yellow">Talk from there.</font>

34
00:03:07,570 --> 00:03:09,370
<font color="yellow">I can't see straight right now.</font>

35
00:03:09,530 --> 00:03:13,100
<font color="yellow">If I can't even touch it, you'll tell me to give everything back.</font>

36
00:03:13,130 --> 00:03:15,500
<font color="yellow">There's nothing I wouldn't do in this desperate situation.</font>

37
00:03:16,230 --> 00:03:19,030
<font color="yellow">What is with this attitude?</font>

38
00:03:19,630 --> 00:03:21,700
<font color="yellow">What if it doesn't work again?</font>

39
00:03:21,700 --> 00:03:25,030
<font color="yellow">If it doesn't work again, there's only one answer.</font>

40
00:03:27,070 --> 00:03:29,270
<font color="yellow">- What? - True love.</font>

41
00:03:32,230 --> 00:03:33,900
<font color="yellow">I'll have to do that too, if necessary!</font>

42
00:03:33,900 --> 00:03:37,730
<font color="yellow">I'd rather love you than lose this bag!</font>

43
00:03:46,930 --> 00:03:48,270
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

44
00:03:50,130 --> 00:03:52,730
<font color="yellow">You put in all that effort and made it snow, too.</font>

45
00:04:00,930 --> 00:04:02,770
<font color="yellow">- Cool. - "Cool"?</font>

46
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:08,100
<font color="yellow">What should I do now?</font>

47
00:04:08,700 --> 00:04:09,770
<font color="yellow">About what?</font>

48
00:04:09,770 --> 00:04:12,030
<font color="yellow">- Will you kick me out? - I won't kick you out!</font>

49
00:04:14,030 --> 00:04:15,170
<font color="yellow">Really?</font>

50
00:04:15,770 --> 00:04:18,030
<font color="yellow">Don't forget what you signed.</font>

51
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:22,770
<font color="yellow">They say, a man's word is worth his weight in gold.</font>

52
00:04:23,740 --> 00:04:25,500
<font color="yellow">Don't be cheap and take it back.</font>

53
00:04:29,430 --> 00:04:33,470
<font color="yellow">My uncle isn't coming back?</font>

54
00:04:34,070 --> 00:04:35,300
<font color="yellow">Wait.</font>

55
00:04:35,570 --> 00:04:39,240
<font color="yellow">Are you saying my uncle left this world?</font>

56
00:04:40,370 --> 00:04:43,470
<font color="yellow">(Registration Certificate)</font>

57
00:04:43,470 --> 00:04:47,430
<font color="yellow">He led an immortal life and is finally perishing.</font>

58
00:04:48,470 --> 00:04:50,370
<font color="yellow">Do not miss him for too long.</font>

59
00:04:50,970 --> 00:04:54,270
<font color="yellow">Death is but a different world on the other side of the door.</font>

60
00:04:54,270 --> 00:04:55,630
<font color="yellow">You will also open that door...</font>

61
00:04:55,630 --> 00:04:58,740
<font color="yellow">No, Uncle. My poor uncle.</font>

62
00:04:58,740 --> 00:05:00,700
<font color="yellow">My poor uncle.</font>

63
00:05:01,430 --> 00:05:03,100
<font color="yellow">I don't need my credit card.</font>

64
00:05:03,470 --> 00:05:05,930
<font color="yellow">I don't need this stupid credit card.</font>

65
00:05:05,930 --> 00:05:08,530
<font color="yellow">Please, come back. Please.</font>

66
00:05:11,700 --> 00:05:12,700
<font color="yellow">What's this?</font>

67
00:05:14,370 --> 00:05:15,870
<font color="yellow">Why is he coming through that door?</font>

68
00:05:16,430 --> 00:05:19,530
<font color="yellow">Uncle! Uncle. Uncle.</font>

69
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:20,870
<font color="yellow">Deok Hwa.</font>

70
00:05:21,500 --> 00:05:22,930
<font color="yellow">Uncle.</font>

71
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:26,030
<font color="yellow">Are you back? Did you come back?</font>

72
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,530
<font color="yellow">I love you, Uncle.</font>

73
00:05:28,530 --> 00:05:29,770
<font color="yellow">Okay, okay.</font>

74
00:05:31,130 --> 00:05:32,600
<font color="yellow">So I was thinking,</font>

75
00:05:33,270 --> 00:05:34,800
<font color="yellow">can I get my credit card back?</font>

76
00:05:38,230 --> 00:05:39,300
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

77
00:05:39,630 --> 00:05:42,300
<font color="yellow">You heard me. Why are you pretending you didn't?</font>

78
00:05:44,130 --> 00:05:45,200
<font color="yellow">Uncle.</font>

79
00:05:48,970 --> 00:05:51,230
<font color="yellow">It's merely a new world on the other side of the door.</font>

80
00:05:51,230 --> 00:05:54,800
<font color="yellow">You've already started the journey. You should just keep going.</font>

81
00:05:55,770 --> 00:05:57,900
<font color="yellow">Deok Hwa is very worried about his uncle.</font>

82
00:05:58,070 --> 00:05:59,830
<font color="yellow">He's right. Don't worry about us.</font>

83
00:05:59,830 --> 00:06:01,670
<font color="yellow">May I get the deed back?</font>

84
00:06:03,670 --> 00:06:05,370
<font color="yellow">What did you do?</font>

85
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:08,000
<font color="yellow">Eun Tak.</font>

86
00:06:10,630 --> 00:06:13,000
<font color="yellow">- Yes? - Please return the 5,000 dollars,</font>

87
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:14,300
<font color="yellow">perfume, and bag first.</font>

88
00:06:14,300 --> 00:06:16,870
<font color="yellow">Uncle. You gave her that much?</font>

89
00:06:18,270 --> 00:06:20,830
<font color="yellow">No. I will not. You said you wouldn't kick me out.</font>

90
00:06:20,830 --> 00:06:23,000
<font color="yellow">I asked for the 5,000 dollars, perfume, and bag.</font>

91
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,930
<font color="yellow">I didn't say I'm kicking you out.</font>

92
00:06:29,830 --> 00:06:31,170
<font color="yellow">Mister.</font>

93
00:06:34,530 --> 00:06:35,700
<font color="yellow">I love you.</font>

94
00:06:39,200 --> 00:06:40,700
<font color="yellow">I love you.</font>

95
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:43,830
<font color="yellow">No?</font>

96
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:49,470
<font color="yellow">I love you, too.</font>

97
00:06:50,430 --> 00:06:51,900
<font color="yellow">- Mister. - Shut it!</font>

98
00:06:51,900 --> 00:06:53,770
<font color="yellow">- I love you. - How dare you?</font>

99
00:06:55,730 --> 00:06:59,470
<font color="yellow">Did you burn the scroll by any chance?</font>

100
00:07:01,530 --> 00:07:04,600
<font color="yellow">- I did. - You are such the jokester.</font>

101
00:07:06,670 --> 00:07:08,170
<font color="yellow">Are you anxious?</font>

102
00:07:08,270 --> 00:07:11,830
<font color="yellow">That's your punishment for being so thorough with your goodbyes.</font>

103
00:07:12,270 --> 00:07:13,430
<font color="yellow">I shall accept it gladly.</font>

104
00:07:13,530 --> 00:07:16,370
<font color="yellow">I shall send the scroll...</font>

105
00:07:16,370 --> 00:07:19,200
<font color="yellow">through Deok Hwa in the morning,</font>

106
00:07:19,300 --> 00:07:21,800
<font color="yellow">so do not worry.</font>

107
00:07:22,170 --> 00:07:23,870
<font color="yellow">Thank you, and I'm sorry.</font>

108
00:07:24,330 --> 00:07:25,970
<font color="yellow">Then Sir,</font>

109
00:07:26,770 --> 00:07:28,770
<font color="yellow">if I dare make a suggestion,</font>

110
00:07:28,970 --> 00:07:30,830
<font color="yellow">could you give up trying to die...</font>

111
00:07:30,830 --> 00:07:33,630
<font color="yellow">and consider living instead?</font>

112
00:07:34,170 --> 00:07:37,330
<font color="yellow">Because of you, some people in the past...</font>

113
00:07:37,330 --> 00:07:39,930
<font color="yellow">were able to turn a new leaf.</font>

114
00:07:40,370 --> 00:07:43,500
<font color="yellow">Wouldn't it be nice if they were to benefit from...</font>

115
00:07:43,700 --> 00:07:45,330
<font color="yellow">a strange but beautiful...</font>

116
00:07:45,330 --> 00:07:48,070
<font color="yellow">stroke of luck or a miracle?</font>

117
00:08:05,130 --> 00:08:07,100
<font color="yellow">A man who never ages...</font>

118
00:08:36,070 --> 00:08:37,570
<font color="yellow">At the age of 29,</font>

119
00:08:38,800 --> 00:08:40,230
<font color="yellow">you're still shining.</font>

120
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,630
<font color="yellow">But I'm not...</font>

121
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:47,130
<font color="yellow">by your side.</font>

122
00:08:55,100 --> 00:08:57,870
<font color="yellow">Why can't I grab it?</font>

123
00:08:58,170 --> 00:09:00,230
<font color="yellow">I can see it but I can't pull it out.</font>

124
00:09:03,470 --> 00:09:05,500
<font color="yellow">Has the future changed...</font>

125
00:09:05,500 --> 00:09:07,570
<font color="yellow">or has the oracle?</font>

126
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:13,230
<font color="yellow">Whatever the case,</font>

127
00:09:15,230 --> 00:09:16,840
<font color="yellow">it is good to be back.</font>

128
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:20,200
<font color="yellow">I'm so shameless.</font>

129
00:09:29,170 --> 00:09:30,470
<font color="yellow">Missing soul.</font>

130
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:34,670
<font color="yellow">Tell me in detail what happened.</font>

131
00:09:40,470 --> 00:09:43,000
<font color="yellow">It started off really well.</font>

132
00:09:43,100 --> 00:09:45,300
<font color="yellow">We were in a moonlit buckwheat field...</font>

133
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:46,970
<font color="yellow">with the first snow falling.</font>

134
00:09:47,570 --> 00:09:50,130
<font color="yellow">Anyway, I tried to hold the sword.</font>

135
00:09:50,730 --> 00:09:51,730
<font color="yellow">However,</font>

136
00:09:52,470 --> 00:09:54,730
<font color="yellow">I couldn't touch it although I could see it.</font>

137
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:57,270
<font color="yellow">He came back alive.</font>

138
00:09:57,430 --> 00:09:59,100
<font color="yellow">I thought one of you wouldn't.</font>

139
00:09:59,100 --> 00:10:01,800
<font color="yellow">I know. I thought he'd leave me in the field.</font>

140
00:10:01,800 --> 00:10:03,200
<font color="yellow">He brought me back.</font>

141
00:10:05,030 --> 00:10:08,130
<font color="yellow">The missing soul does not know yet...</font>

142
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:11,930
<font color="yellow">about what will happen when she pulls out his sword.</font>

143
00:10:13,100 --> 00:10:15,340
<font color="yellow">Should I tell her what will happen?</font>

144
00:10:16,130 --> 00:10:18,600
<font color="yellow">The goblin might die of fury.</font>

145
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:21,130
<font color="yellow">Then this house will be mine.</font>

146
00:10:21,570 --> 00:10:23,670
<font color="yellow">What are you thinking?</font>

147
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,900
<font color="yellow">When you look at me like that,</font>

148
00:10:26,800 --> 00:10:27,970
<font color="yellow">it gives me the chills.</font>

149
00:10:27,970 --> 00:10:29,900
<font color="yellow">Why can't you touch the sword...</font>

150
00:10:29,900 --> 00:10:31,570
<font color="yellow">although you can see it?</font>

151
00:10:32,670 --> 00:10:34,300
<font color="yellow">I was trying to figure it out.</font>

152
00:10:34,300 --> 00:10:36,030
<font color="yellow">You, too? So was I.</font>

153
00:10:36,700 --> 00:10:37,900
<font color="yellow">Why is that?</font>

154
00:10:39,430 --> 00:10:41,000
<font color="yellow">Is the goblin right?</font>

155
00:10:41,500 --> 00:10:43,970
<font color="yellow">Am I really not his bride?</font>

156
00:10:44,340 --> 00:10:48,130
<font color="yellow">Is there another bride who can touch the sword...</font>

157
00:10:48,270 --> 00:10:49,470
<font color="yellow">and will she be pretty?</font>

158
00:10:52,300 --> 00:10:54,230
<font color="yellow">Anyone could do the deed.</font>

159
00:10:55,300 --> 00:10:56,340
<font color="yellow">Exactly.</font>

160
00:10:57,030 --> 00:10:59,270
<font color="yellow">Do you think he'd go back to being mean to me?</font>

161
00:10:59,270 --> 00:11:00,800
<font color="yellow">We're pretty close now.</font>

162
00:11:10,030 --> 00:11:13,030
<font color="yellow">One extra mouth to feed is really taxing our expenses.</font>

163
00:11:16,500 --> 00:11:18,570
<font color="yellow">We're out of meat already.</font>

164
00:11:18,670 --> 00:11:20,800
<font color="yellow">Should I start keeping track of receipts?</font>

165
00:11:24,430 --> 00:11:27,170
<font color="yellow">I'm in too rotten a mood to do the dishes.</font>

166
00:11:29,270 --> 00:11:31,170
<font color="yellow">I'll do the dishes.</font>

167
00:11:31,430 --> 00:11:33,930
<font color="yellow">I really want to do the dishes.</font>

168
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,200
<font color="yellow">Do you?</font>

169
00:11:35,700 --> 00:11:39,300
<font color="yellow">I guess you are at the age where you'd love to do the dishes.</font>

170
00:11:45,230 --> 00:11:47,970
<font color="yellow">There's so much washing to do.</font>

171
00:11:48,870 --> 00:11:52,270
<font color="yellow">I can't afford to send everything to the dry cleaner's.</font>

172
00:11:52,430 --> 00:11:54,500
<font color="yellow">Should I throw out all my dirty clothes?</font>

173
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:58,470
<font color="yellow">You have me. As soon as I'm done with the dishes,</font>

174
00:11:58,470 --> 00:12:00,370
<font color="yellow">I could do the laundry.</font>

175
00:12:00,370 --> 00:12:02,830
<font color="yellow">Will you do that? If you insist,</font>

176
00:12:03,100 --> 00:12:04,630
<font color="yellow">I prefer them to be hand-washed.</font>

177
00:12:10,270 --> 00:12:12,870
<font color="yellow">I bet students find it easier to concentrate in a clean home.</font>

178
00:12:14,570 --> 00:12:16,700
<font color="yellow">When will I clean all these rooms?</font>

179
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:20,000
<font color="yellow">I feel bad for the student in the house.</font>

180
00:12:23,370 --> 00:12:25,200
<font color="yellow">Was that deliberate?</font>

181
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,200
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

182
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:29,000
<font color="yellow">I'm wet. You must see that.</font>

183
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:31,130
<font color="yellow">I wonder if they'll dry by this evening.</font>

184
00:12:37,530 --> 00:12:39,630
<font color="yellow">You are doing that deliberately.</font>

185
00:12:39,730 --> 00:12:42,170
<font color="yellow">Do you hate doing the washing? Tell me what's bothering you.</font>

186
00:12:42,170 --> 00:12:44,130
<font color="yellow">I'm glad you brought that up.</font>

187
00:12:44,130 --> 00:12:47,370
<font color="yellow">You must think I'm not your bride.</font>

188
00:12:47,370 --> 00:12:49,570
<font color="yellow">Let's not jump to conclusions.</font>

189
00:12:49,570 --> 00:12:52,400
<font color="yellow">You might seriously regret giving me a hard time.</font>

190
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:55,970
<font color="yellow">Do you mean you are my bride but you can only see my sword?</font>

191
00:12:55,970 --> 00:12:59,730
<font color="yellow">You said every moment you spent with me shined.</font>

192
00:12:59,730 --> 00:13:02,630
<font color="yellow">Because the weather was good, bad,</font>

193
00:13:02,830 --> 00:13:04,500
<font color="yellow">- or good enough. - Yes.</font>

194
00:13:04,830 --> 00:13:06,270
<font color="yellow">- Today as well. - See?</font>

195
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:10,570
<font color="yellow">- What? - Even now.</font>

196
00:13:10,900 --> 00:13:12,600
<font color="yellow">You shine brilliantly.</font>

197
00:13:14,700 --> 00:13:16,200
<font color="yellow">So why are you...</font>

198
00:13:16,700 --> 00:13:18,930
<font color="yellow">- giving me a hard time? - That's different.</font>

199
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:22,470
<font color="yellow">How are they different issues? You said everything shines.</font>

200
00:13:22,700 --> 00:13:25,430
<font color="yellow">Can't we stop doing this?</font>

201
00:13:25,430 --> 00:13:27,270
<font color="yellow">Let's find another value.</font>

202
00:13:27,270 --> 00:13:30,030
<font color="yellow">If I can't be your bride, since you're my boyfriend,</font>

203
00:13:30,030 --> 00:13:32,000
<font color="yellow">I'll be your girlfriend.</font>

204
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:33,100
<font color="yellow">No, thanks.</font>

205
00:13:34,230 --> 00:13:36,230
<font color="yellow">- How about acquaintances? - No.</font>

206
00:13:36,770 --> 00:13:38,570
<font color="yellow">Then a lodger?</font>

207
00:13:38,570 --> 00:13:40,430
<font color="yellow">Then pay 500 dollars a month in rent.</font>

208
00:13:40,430 --> 00:13:42,070
<font color="yellow">Water and gas bills are separate.</font>

209
00:13:43,670 --> 00:13:46,500
<font color="yellow">Did he demand you give him money?</font>

210
00:13:46,730 --> 00:13:48,730
<font color="yellow">Yes. We're at loggerheads now.</font>

211
00:13:48,930 --> 00:13:51,600
<font color="yellow">We're bound to clash sooner or later.</font>

212
00:13:52,130 --> 00:13:53,930
<font color="yellow">Why can't I touch the stupid sword?</font>

213
00:13:53,930 --> 00:13:57,030
<font color="yellow">Maybe you need something more powerful than the curse.</font>

