<font color="yellow">Eating without paying?</font>

845
00:58:51,740 --> 00:58:54,710
<font color="yellow">That's such a crass crime that I've never heard of.</font>

846
00:58:54,810 --> 00:58:56,140
<font color="yellow">Where do I sign?</font>

847
00:58:57,210 --> 00:58:58,910
<font color="yellow">This is who I am.</font>

848
00:59:01,140 --> 00:59:02,170
<font color="yellow">You have...</font>

849
00:59:02,870 --> 00:59:04,040
<font color="yellow">a business card?</font>

850
00:59:15,370 --> 00:59:17,440
<font color="yellow">What's going on? Why do you have a business card?</font>

851
00:59:17,440 --> 00:59:18,540
<font color="yellow">Uncle.</font>

852
00:59:19,340 --> 00:59:21,110
<font color="yellow">- Have some tofu. - Did you know?</font>

853
00:59:21,210 --> 00:59:22,640
<font color="yellow">He has a business card.</font>

854
00:59:22,940 --> 00:59:25,140
<font color="yellow">A business card? Of course he does.</font>

855
00:59:25,470 --> 00:59:26,740
<font color="yellow">He owns the whole company.</font>

856
00:59:26,740 --> 00:59:29,370
<font color="yellow">Hotel, trading, ship-building, oil, construction, and furniture.</font>

857
00:59:29,370 --> 00:59:32,240
<font color="yellow">- Didn't you know? - Stop it. I didn't tell him.</font>

858
00:59:32,240 --> 00:59:33,770
<font color="yellow">That's how rich I am.</font>

859
00:59:34,010 --> 00:59:36,310
<font color="yellow">Here, have some tofu.</font>

860
00:59:36,570 --> 00:59:38,140
<font color="yellow">I've always wanted to do this.</font>

861
00:59:38,370 --> 00:59:41,570
<font color="yellow">Like uncle, like nephew. Get out of my way.</font>

862
00:59:45,040 --> 00:59:47,210
<font color="yellow">Why does he always walk like that?</font>

863
00:59:49,210 --> 00:59:52,110
<font color="yellow">I got it. I finally figured it out.</font>

864
00:59:52,620 --> 00:59:54,450
<font color="yellow">He sees something when he touches someone.</font>

865
00:59:54,590 --> 00:59:56,060
<font color="yellow">The person's previous life.</font>

866
00:59:57,980 --> 00:59:59,750
<font color="yellow">He can see someone's past life?</font>

867
01:00:00,020 --> 01:00:02,720
<font color="yellow">What about you? What kind of power do you have?</font>

868
01:00:02,740 --> 01:00:04,510
<font color="yellow">My power is staying alive.</font>

869
01:00:06,420 --> 01:00:08,980
<font color="yellow">You can't do anything but make it rain, can you?</font>

870
01:00:10,780 --> 01:00:12,180
<font color="yellow">You forgot your tofu.</font>

871
01:00:33,650 --> 01:00:36,080
<font color="yellow">I guess the missing soul isn't back yet.</font>

872
01:00:36,320 --> 01:00:37,950
<font color="yellow">Is she out with him?</font>

873
01:00:38,750 --> 01:00:40,680
<font color="yellow">- Hello? - Where are you?</font>

874
01:00:40,920 --> 01:00:43,220
<font color="yellow">Why aren't you back yet? It's scary out there at night.</font>

875
01:00:43,220 --> 01:00:46,220
<font color="yellow">It's only 7pm, and I'm busy right now.</font>

876
01:00:46,680 --> 01:00:48,280
<font color="yellow">Hello?</font>

877
01:00:53,150 --> 01:00:56,220
<font color="yellow">The phone has been turned off.</font>

878
01:00:56,220 --> 01:00:57,320
<font color="yellow">Please leave a message...</font>

879
01:00:57,320 --> 01:00:58,650
<font color="yellow">Unbelievable.</font>

880
01:01:06,680 --> 01:01:08,880
<font color="yellow">Which of you saw the goblin's bride?</font>

881
01:01:10,020 --> 01:01:11,050
<font color="yellow">Where?</font>

882
01:01:11,180 --> 01:01:12,320
<font color="yellow">Uncle!</font>

883
01:01:14,420 --> 01:01:15,420
<font color="yellow">Uncle.</font>

884
01:01:18,350 --> 01:01:19,880
<font color="yellow">He's not in. He went out.</font>

885
01:01:19,880 --> 01:01:21,220
<font color="yellow">Did he?</font>

886
01:01:21,950 --> 01:01:23,920
<font color="yellow">Then can you pass this to him?</font>

887
01:01:23,920 --> 01:01:25,550
<font color="yellow">I forgot that it was in my car.</font>

888
01:01:27,780 --> 01:01:30,420
<font color="yellow">Why give him this when he took your credit card?</font>

889
01:01:30,420 --> 01:01:32,680
<font color="yellow">My grandpa said he'd give me an allowance if I deliver this.</font>

890
01:01:32,750 --> 01:01:34,950
<font color="yellow">- You humans... - That's how scary...</font>

891
01:01:34,950 --> 01:01:36,580
<font color="yellow">and convenient capitalism is.</font>

892
01:01:38,850 --> 01:01:42,880
<font color="yellow">He gave you a credit card and me the deed to the house.</font>

893
01:01:43,480 --> 01:01:46,220
<font color="yellow">He must've given your grandfather something more valuable.</font>

894
01:01:46,520 --> 01:01:47,620
<font color="yellow">Do you think so?</font>

895
01:01:47,980 --> 01:01:51,120
<font color="yellow">I don't know what this is. Shall we have a look?</font>

896
01:01:51,150 --> 01:01:52,320
<font color="yellow">He isn't here.</font>

897
01:01:56,150 --> 01:01:57,650
<font color="yellow">She's really pretty.</font>

898
01:02:17,580 --> 01:02:20,680
<font color="yellow">Who is she? Is she his ex-girlfriend?</font>

899
01:02:21,720 --> 01:02:23,750
<font color="yellow">This looks really old.</font>

900
01:02:24,350 --> 01:02:25,380
<font color="yellow">Doesn't it?</font>

901
01:02:51,450 --> 01:02:52,850
<font color="yellow">What's wrong?</font>

902
01:04:14,480 --> 01:04:18,620
<font color="yellow">It was the beginning of a terribly sad love story.</font>

903
01:04:20,420 --> 01:04:23,620
<font color="yellow">This thing called destiny is so sad.</font>

904
01:04:25,750 --> 01:04:28,580
<font color="yellow">It's not a sin to fall in love.</font>

905
01:04:28,650 --> 01:04:31,850
<font color="yellow">Maybe they didn't deserve what they got.</font>

906
01:04:35,150 --> 01:04:39,250
<font color="yellow">What did I do to deserve a sudden raise in rent?</font>

907
01:04:39,280 --> 01:04:42,750
<font color="yellow">I can't afford to pay an extra 100 dollars a month.</font>

908
01:04:42,980 --> 01:04:44,580
<font color="yellow">Ever since you moved in,</font>

909
01:04:44,880 --> 01:04:47,580
<font color="yellow">I keep dreaming of grim reapers.</font>

910
01:04:49,550 --> 01:04:50,580
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

911
01:04:50,880 --> 01:04:54,750
<font color="yellow">The tap in my bathroom is leaking. When will you fix it?</font>

912
01:04:54,750 --> 01:04:57,150
<font color="yellow">Is it leaking? Then don't shower.</font>

913
01:04:57,550 --> 01:04:59,180
<font color="yellow">You'll still be pretty.</font>

914
01:06:08,420 --> 01:06:09,550
<font color="yellow">You can sing.</font>

915
01:06:11,420 --> 01:06:12,420
<font color="yellow">I know.</font>

916
01:06:13,580 --> 01:06:15,120
<font color="yellow">How did you know I'd be here?</font>

917
01:06:16,880 --> 01:06:19,180
<font color="yellow">You can run but you can't hide.</font>

918
01:06:19,790 --> 01:06:21,520
<font color="yellow">What about the chicken place? Did you get fired?</font>

919
01:06:21,720 --> 01:06:23,550
<font color="yellow">I'm working multiple jobs now.</font>

920
01:06:23,720 --> 01:06:25,250
<font color="yellow">Singing at weddings pays well.</font>

921
01:06:26,820 --> 01:06:27,820
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

922
01:06:28,680 --> 01:06:30,450
<font color="yellow">watching wedding ceremonies...</font>

923
01:06:30,650 --> 01:06:32,220
<font color="yellow">makes me feel strange.</font>

924
01:06:33,250 --> 01:06:34,350
<font color="yellow">Why do you feel strange?</font>

925
01:06:35,180 --> 01:06:36,180
<font color="yellow">Just...</font>

926
01:06:37,950 --> 01:06:40,650
<font color="yellow">"I won't have a mom to light the candles..."</font>

927
01:06:42,880 --> 01:06:45,250
<font color="yellow">"or a dad to hold my hand."</font>

928
01:06:46,050 --> 01:06:48,380
<font color="yellow">"I won't have friends to take pictures of me."</font>

929
01:06:48,850 --> 01:06:51,950
<font color="yellow">"Without any friends, there won't be any congratulatory money."</font>

930
01:06:52,520 --> 01:06:53,790
<font color="yellow">Such thoughts come to my mind.</font>

931
01:06:55,050 --> 01:06:56,050
<font color="yellow">It's funny, right?</font>

932
01:06:57,650 --> 01:06:58,680
<font color="yellow">That's probably why...</font>

933
01:07:01,180 --> 01:07:03,620
<font color="yellow">I was obsessed with being your bride.</font>

934
01:07:04,850 --> 01:07:06,750
<font color="yellow">It felt like we were becoming family.</font>

935
01:07:09,250 --> 01:07:12,320
<font color="yellow">I thought I could have what I never had.</font>

936
01:07:16,350 --> 01:07:18,380
<font color="yellow">I thought it came to me like fate.</font>

937
01:07:27,020 --> 01:07:29,580
<font color="yellow">Why... Why are you crying?</font>

938
01:07:30,920 --> 01:07:32,250
<font color="yellow">Are you trying to make me feel sorry?</font>

939
01:07:33,550 --> 01:07:34,550
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

940
01:07:35,850 --> 01:07:37,120
<font color="yellow">In the end,</font>

941
01:07:37,580 --> 01:07:39,080
<font color="yellow">I should be the one who's sorry.</font>

942
01:07:40,320 --> 01:07:41,550
<font color="yellow">You know what?</font>

943
01:07:43,350 --> 01:07:45,150
<font color="yellow">I'm really sorry.</font>

944
01:07:46,380 --> 01:07:47,980
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry I couldn't draw the sword.</font>

945
01:07:50,050 --> 01:07:51,880
<font color="yellow">I've been meaning to tell you,</font>

946
01:07:52,450 --> 01:07:55,050
<font color="yellow">but every time we met, we got into an argument.</font>

947
01:07:58,580 --> 01:08:00,450
<font color="yellow">I know this isn't the perfect timing,</font>

948
01:08:01,380 --> 01:08:03,180
<font color="yellow">but I should say it now that we're talking about it.</font>

949
01:08:04,980 --> 01:08:08,120
<font color="yellow">I'm working more jobs...</font>

950
01:08:08,220 --> 01:08:10,320
<font color="yellow">and steadily preparing myself.</font>

951
01:08:10,790 --> 01:08:14,880
<font color="yellow">So can you wait a little longer until I leave the house?</font>

952
01:08:15,320 --> 01:08:16,680
<font color="yellow">Stop being mean to me.</font>

953
01:08:19,750 --> 01:08:21,790
<font color="yellow">Until I'm ready to leave,</font>

954
01:08:22,720 --> 01:08:24,290
<font color="yellow">can you give me a 50 percent discount...</font>

955
01:08:25,320 --> 01:08:27,950
<font color="yellow">when you're being mean to me? Please?</font>

956
01:08:50,080 --> 01:08:51,720
<font color="yellow">I don't think I can do that.</font>

957
01:08:53,350 --> 01:08:54,920
<font color="yellow">Not the 50 percent discount.</font>

958
01:09:06,720 --> 01:09:08,380
<font color="yellow">45 percent?</font>

959
01:09:20,180 --> 01:09:22,080
<font color="yellow">What is it? Are you hurt?</font>

960
01:09:23,080 --> 01:09:24,650
<font color="yellow">Is it the sword?</font>

961
01:09:54,350 --> 01:09:55,350
<font color="yellow">Mister.</font>

962
01:09:58,290 --> 01:09:59,620
<font color="yellow">I can grab the sword.</font>

963
01:10:03,820 --> 01:10:05,020
<font color="yellow">Hold on.</font>

964
01:10:06,680 --> 01:10:08,850
<font color="yellow">Hold on. I'll pull it out for you.</font>

965
01:10:14,980 --> 01:10:16,020
<font color="yellow">It's moving.</font>

966
01:11:00,180 --> 01:11:01,950
<font color="yellow">The oracle was real.</font>

967
01:11:05,520 --> 01:11:07,650
<font color="yellow">The future I foresaw was correct.</font>

968
01:11:10,220 --> 01:11:12,080
<font color="yellow">With this girl's help,</font>

969
01:11:14,220 --> 01:11:16,320
<font color="yellow">I'll be able to end this curse of eternity...</font>

970
01:11:18,650 --> 01:11:20,680
<font color="yellow">and return to ashes.</font>

971
01:11:28,720 --> 01:11:30,650
<font color="yellow">A mortal soul can only live up to 100 years.</font>

972
01:11:32,180 --> 01:11:34,720
<font color="yellow">Is what I'm looking for...</font>

973
01:11:36,320 --> 01:11:38,120
<font color="yellow">my life as an immortal soul...</font>

974
01:11:39,980 --> 01:11:41,450
<font color="yellow">or your face?</font>

975
01:11:46,250 --> 01:11:47,920
<font color="yellow">I think it's your face.</font>

976
01:12:32,550 --> 01:12:35,520
<font color="yellow">(Goblin)</font>

977
01:12:36,450 --> 01:12:39,720
<font color="yellow">I told you. I really am your bride.</font>

978
01:12:40,020 --> 01:12:42,080
<font color="yellow">This was destined to happen.</font>

979
01:12:42,680 --> 01:12:43,680
<font color="yellow">It was destiny.</font>

980
01:12:44,580 --> 01:12:45,680
<font color="yellow">It's nice.</font>

981
01:12:48,680 --> 01:12:50,450
<font color="yellow">Who on earth are you?</font>

982
01:12:51,620 --> 01:12:53,480
<font color="yellow">Why are you making me feel smoldered?</font>

983
01:12:58,950 --> 01:13:00,480
<font color="yellow">I think I saw her from somewhere.</font>

984
01:13:01,980 --> 01:13:04,650
<font color="yellow">How did you remember your past life?</font>

985
01:13:08,450 --> 01:13:10,790
<font color="yellow">One day after 100 years...</font>

986
01:13:11,150 --> 01:13:12,920
<font color="yellow">When the weather is good enough...</font>

987
01:13:15,350 --> 01:13:17,420
<font color="yellow">One day after 100 years...</font>

988
01:13:18,950 --> 01:13:20,880
<font color="yellow">When the weather is good enough,</font>

989
01:13:22,320 --> 01:13:25,820
<font color="yellow">I wish I could tell her that she was my first love.</font>

990
01:13:27,850 --> 01:13:31,120
<font color="yellow">I ask for permission to be granted.</font>

